<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-1931] Radial shading is missing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1931</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The attached file contains a radial shading fill which is missing. RadialShadingContext#calculateInputValues is returning NaN which seems to be incorrect.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12696480">PDFBOX-1931</key>
            <summary>Radial shading is missing</summary>
